node CPS · Crime + Punishment in Suburbia · ⟦Fred Skolnik:CPS:9f5419⟧

the carbon character is the program; this file is its User — the actor who lent the face.

the program (in-world) : Fred Skolnik — the stepfather · the abuser, the victim
the User (carbon)      : Michael Ironside  [ the actor, 2000 film ]
the analog (your world): the domestic tyrant — the abuser whose death the story dares you to mourn
the resemblance        : Ironside brings menace to the alcoholic stepfather whose violence sets the tragedy in motion.
seal (program)         : I am the reason she killed — which is exactly why this isn't Dostoevsky: his victim was harmless, and mine made the axe feel like mercy.

